Use the format: "Activity Digest - [date range]" where the date range will be provided in the user prompt.

**Issue Description:**
- Include the complete activity digest content
- Maintain all formatting, links, and structure from the original digest
- Add a header explaining this is an automated activity digest
- Include any relevant labels or metadata

**Labels to Apply:**
- "activity-digest"
- "documentation"
- "automated"

